skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: scope travel
des: Scope Travel's official Alexa Skill. We strive to publish our rich travel content across every platform. Use Alexa to ask for a list of featured posts or have Alexa read a particular post to you. In the future, we will expand our skill to allow access to even more of our content. We hope you enjoy and please provide feedback that you may have. Visit www.scope.travel to read and experience the rest of our content
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
